#: src/mathlib.c:1033
#, c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"* Notice: \"%s\" was selected, but you can only change to a\n"
"* different Intel MKL threading library by restarting xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* However, you may continue to select any other Linear Algebra library\n"
"* without restart, including this same Intel MKL library.  All other\n"
"* Intel MKL threading libraries are disabled until restart because of an \n"
"* MKL limitation where the MKL threading library can only be dynamically\n"
"* linked only once per runtime.\n"
"* \n"
"* See Intel's documentation on mkl_set_threading_layer() for more detail.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"* Merknad: \"%s\" ble valgt, men du kan bare endre til et\n"
"* annet Intel MKL-trådbibliotek ved å starte xnec2c på nytt.\n"
"* \n"
"* Du kan imidlertid fortsette å velge et annet Lineært Algebrabibliotek\n"
"* uten omstart, inkludert dette samme Intel MKL-biblioteket.  Alle andre\n"
"* Intel MKL-trådbiblioteker er deaktivert frem til omstart på grunn av en\n"
"* MKL-begrensning der MKL-trådbiblioteket bare kan kobles dynamisk\n"
"* én gang per kjøretid.\n"
"* \n"
"* Se Intels dokumentasjon om mkl_set_threading_layer() for mer detaljer.\n"

